### Meteo France Public API
### Base URL: https://public-api.meteofrance.fr
### Authentication: API Key (JWT token)
### Rate Limit: 50 requests per minute

### List all massifs
GET https://public-api.meteofrance.fr/public/DPBRA/v1/liste-massifs
Content-Type: application/json
apikey: {{meteofrance_api_key}}
User-Agent: axios/1.6.0

###
### Get BRA (Bulletin d'estimation du Risque d'Avalanche) - XML Format
### Example massif IDs: 1=Chablais, 2=Aravis, 3=Mont-Blanc
GET https://public-api.meteofrance.fr/public/DPBRA/massif/BRA?id-massif=4&format=xml
Content-Type: application/xml
apikey: {{meteofrance_api_key}}
User-Agent: axios/1.6.0

###
### Get BRA - PDF Format
GET https://public-api.meteofrance.fr/public/DPBRA/v1/massif/BRA?id-massif=3&format=pdf
Content-Type: application/pdf
apikey: {{meteofrance_api_key}}
User-Agent: axios/1.6.0

